Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE Limited presents the opportunity to lease units 2 & 4 at 12500 Vickers Way in Richmond, BC. This combined ground floor warehouse unit is located in a an industrial/retail building in Richmond’s home improvement hub, offering approximately 7,174 of rentable square footage. The property boasts 12’ ceilings, heavy power, ample parking in front for tenants and visitors, and is sprinklered throughout. Paired with IR1 zoning, this warehouse offers great flexibility for a wide array of potential tenants.
